				"number": "8",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"74246\"></a>Indikationer för nutritionsbehandling  vid <a class=\"index\" id=\"1034874\" data-text=\"KOL:undern&#xE4;ring\"></a>KOL<sup><a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_31\"><sup>a</sup></a></sup>",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><ul><li><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><span class=\"tabstop\"></span>Ingen viktnedgång<span class=\"tab\"></span>0 p<br>Viktnedgång senaste 2 månaderna<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>1 p<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span></li></ul><ul><li><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><span class=\"tabstop\"></span>Oförändrad eller ökad aptit<span class=\"tab\"></span>0 p<br>Minskad aptit<span class=\"tab\"></span> senaste 2 månaderna<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>1 p</li></ul><ul><li><span class=\"tabstop\"></span><span class=\"tabstop\"></span>BMI &gt;&nbsp;20 kg/m<sup>2<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span></sup>0 p<br>BMI 18–20 kg/m<sup>2<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span></sup>1 p<br>BMI &lt;&nbsp;18 kg/m<sup>2<span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span></sup>2 p</li></ul><p>Om summan blir <span>≥</span>&nbsp;2 poäng behöver <br>patienten kvalificerad hjälp med sin nutrition.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_31\">a. Nationellt vårdprogram för KOL, <a href=\"http://www.slmf.se/kol\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">www.slmf.se/kol</a> .</div></td></tr></tbody></table>",
